                        <!-- WELCOME -->
                        <Border Background="#f0fdf4" BorderBrush="#bbf7d0" BorderThickness="1" CornerRadius="8" Padding="20" Margin="0,0,0,15">
                            <StackPanel>
                                <TextBlock Text="Welcome to Daily Prayer Timer" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="20" Foreground="#166534" Margin="0,0,0,8"/>
                                <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="13" Foreground="#374151" LineHeight="22">
                                    Assalamu Alaikum! Daily Prayer Timer is a full-featured Windows application designed to help you stay connected with your daily prayers and spiritual journey. Whether you are at home, at work, or on the go, this app gives you accurate prayer times based on your exact location, sends you timely reminders, and helps you track your spiritual progress day by day. It runs quietly in your system tray, integrates with your Windows taskbar, and is built to be both powerful and unobtrusive.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>
                        </Border>

                        <!-- HOME TAB -->
                        <Border Background="#f0f9ff" BorderBrush="#bae6fd" BorderThickness="1" CornerRadius="8" Padding="15" Margin="0,0,0,12">
                            <StackPanel>
                                <TextBlock Text="🏠 Home Tab — At a Glance" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="17" Foreground="#0369a1" Margin="0,0,0,8"/>
                                <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12.5" Foreground="#374151" LineHeight="21">
When you open the app, the Home tab is where the magic happens. At the top, you will see the Hero Card — a beautiful glassmorphic panel that shows your current prayer, a live countdown ticking down to the next prayer, and key times like Sunrise and Sunset flanked on the sides. This card is the heart of the app.
                                </TextBlock>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,6,0,2">
                                    <BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                        <TextBlock Text="🕌" FontSize="12"/>
                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Live Countdown:</Bold> The timer updates every second so you always know how much time remains before the next prayer. During Ramadan, it intelligently switches to "Time Left for Iftar" during Asr.</TextBlock>
                                </BulletDecorator>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,3,0,2">
                                    <BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                        <TextBlock Text="⭐" FontSize="12"/>
                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Daily Highlights:</Bold> Below the hero you get quick cards showing Suhur time, Iftar time, and today's fasting status (if you are fasting). These cards are context-aware and change based on the time of day.</TextBlock>
                                </BulletDecorator>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,3,0,2">
                                    <BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                        <TextBlock Text="🌙" FontSize="12"/>
                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Hijri Date:</Bold> The current Islamic date is shown alongside the Gregorian date, fetched from reliable API data with smart offline fallback.</TextBlock>
                                </BulletDecorator>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,3,0,2">
                                    <BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                        <TextBlock Text="👤" FontSize="12"/>
                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Immersive Modes:</Bold> Press <Bold>F11</Bold> for full-screen mode that hides the taskbar and all UI chrome. Click the Zen Mode toggle (✨ icon) for a minimalist view focused purely on the countdown.</TextBlock>
