                                <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12.5" Foreground="#374151" LineHeight="21">
The Salat tab gives you a complete list of today's prayer times in a clean, scrollable view. Every prayer — Fajr, Sunrise, Dhuhr, Asr, Maghrib, and Isha — is displayed as a premium card with its start time, end time, and a visual status indicator. The active prayer is highlighted prominently so you can spot it instantly.
                                </TextBlock>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,6,0,2">
                                    <BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                        <TextBlock Text="🔔" FontSize="12"/>
                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Nafal Prayers:</Bold> Salat al-Duha (mid-morning) and Tahajjud (last third of the night) are automatically shown in their respective time windows, along with guidance on their preferred timing.</TextBlock>
                                </BulletDecorator>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,3,0,2">
