                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Prohibited Times (Makruh):</Bold> Three time windows when prayer is discouraged — Sunrise, Zawal (noon), and Sunset — are displayed at the bottom with countdowns and clear warnings. Tooltips explain why these times are significant.</TextBlock>
                                </BulletDecorator>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,3,0,2">
                                    <BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                        <TextBlock Text="📋" FontSize="12"/>
                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Rakat Info:</Bold> Each prayer card shows the breakdown of Sunnah, Fard, and Nafl rakats so you know exactly what to pray.</TextBlock>
