                        <!-- TRACKER TAB -->
                        <Border Background="#f5f3ff" BorderBrush="#ddd6fe" BorderThickness="1" CornerRadius="8" Padding="15" Margin="0,0,0,12">
                            <StackPanel>
                                <TextBlock Text="📊 Tracker Tab — Your Spiritual Journal" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="17" Foreground="#5b21b6" Margin="0,0,0,8"/>
                                <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12.5" Foreground="#374151" LineHeight="21">
The Tracker is your personal spiritual diary. It records which prayers you have prayed each day, helps you track missed (Qadha) prayers, and gives you beautiful analytics showing your consistency over weeks, months, and years.
                                </TextBlock>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,6,0,2">
                                    <BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                        <TextBlock Text="✅" FontSize="12"/>
                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Daily Check-in:</Bold> Tap each prayer to mark it as prayed. The app automatically identifies missed prayers as Qadha once the next prayer time begins. You can also log Nafal prayers like Tahajjud, Duha, and Awwabin.</TextBlock>
                                </BulletDecorator>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,3,0,2">
                                    <BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                        <TextBlock Text="📈" FontSize="12"/>
                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Analytics:</Bold> See your completion percentage for this week, month, and year at a glance. The progress cards show "Completed" vs "Missed" counts so you can track your improvement over time.</TextBlock>
                                </BulletDecorator>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,3,0,2">
                                    <BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                        <TextBlock Text="💪" FontSize="12"/>
                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Deeds Logging:</Bold> Have you done something good today? Log spiritual deeds alongside your prayers — giving charity, reading Quran, helping someone, etc. After each prayer's Jamaat time, a popup gently reminds you to log your deeds.</TextBlock>
                                </BulletDecorator>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,3,0,2">
                                    <BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                        <TextBlock Text="🔄" FontSize="12"/>
                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Daily Summary:</Bold> At a scheduled time each night (default 10:00 PM), the app shows a popup summarizing your day — which prayers you prayed, which you missed, and your deeds. You can adjust this time or disable it in Settings.</TextBlock>
                                </BulletDecorator>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,3,0,2">
                                    <BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                        <TextBlock Text="💾" FontSize="12"/>
                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Backup &amp; Restore:</Bold> Never lose your data. You can manually backup your tracker data as a ZIP file, restore from a backup, or set up automatic daily/weekly/monthly backups to a folder of your choice.</TextBlock>
