                                <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12.5" Foreground="#374151" LineHeight="21">
The Qibla compass helps you find the exact direction of the Kaaba in Makkah from your current location. It uses spherical trigonometry to calculate the precise bearing and displays it visually with a beautiful compass rose.
                                </TextBlock>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,6,0,2">
