                                <TextBlock Text="📿 Tasbih Tab — Dhikr &amp; Duas" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="17" Foreground="#166534" Margin="0,0,0,8"/>
                                <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12.5" Foreground="#374151" LineHeight="21">
The Tasbih tab has two modes: a digital Dhikr counter and a Dua library. Tap the tab header to switch between them.
                                </TextBlock>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,6,0,2">
                                    <BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                        <TextBlock Text="📿" FontSize="12"/>
                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Dhikr Counter:</Bold> Five phrases — SubhanAllah, Alhamdulillah, Allahu Akbar, La ilaha illallah, Astaghfirullah. Tap the big button or press Space/Enter to count. Hit the target number and it snaps back to zero with a satisfying animation. Decrement and reset buttons are always there. Your daily totals are saved automatically.</TextBlock>
                                </BulletDecorator>
                                <BulletDecorator Margin="0,3,0,2">
                                    <BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                        <TextBlock Text="📖" FontSize="12"/>
                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Dua Library:</Bold> 26 after-salaam duas plus the Witr salaam dua, each shown in a clean accordion card with the full Arabic text, transliteration, and translation in both English and Bangla. Tap a card to expand it. Use the language toggle to switch between English and Bangla translations.</TextBlock>
