                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Daily Dua:</Bold> A curated set of 10 duas that rotate daily — each with Arabic, transliteration, and translation. A new dua appears each day of Ramadan.</TextBlock>
