                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Spiritual Goal:</Bold> Set a daily spiritual goal. Mark it complete for a satisfying strikethrough. View your last 7 days of goals in the history section.</TextBlock>
