                                    </BulletDecorator.Bullet>
                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Laylatul Qadr Tracker:</Bold> During the last 10 nights (Ramadan 21-30), mark which nights you observed. Each night shows its corresponding Gregorian date for easy reference.</TextBlock>
