                                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="12" Foreground="#374151" Margin="10,0,0,0"><Bold>Eid Takbeer Notification:</Bold> Enable this toggle to receive a Windows toast notification on Eid day (Shawwal 1) with the full Takbeer text, calculated using the UmAlQura calendar.</TextBlock>
